      <hedline>
        <hl1>THE GREAT ALASKA DEBATE</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Timothy Egan's article "The Great Alaska Debate: Can Oil and Wilderness Mix?" (Aug. 4) was excellent.</p>
        <p>Drilling for oil in the Arctic isn't the real issue -- the real issue regards the American spirit. At what cost will we further destroy the delicate and fragile beauty of the planet? We must seriously investigate alternative and renewable energy sources. It's no secret that time is running out. ALEXANDRA ELLEN APPEL Jay Peak, Vt.</p>
      </block>
